-- 11. Sevenoaks × AI Automation
INSERT INTO public.local_content (service_slug, town_slug, intro_paragraph, local_context, competition_landscape, success_approach, local_stats, pain_points, solutions, faqs, layout_variant)
VALUES (
  'ai-automation',
  'sevenoaks',
  'Sevenoaks businesses face a particular paradox. The affluent market commands premium prices but also demands premium service levels that place enormous strain on small teams. A solicitor on the High Street handles complex casework while also managing client communications, compliance documentation, and billing. A specialist contractor serving properties around Knole House juggles project management, materials procurement, and customer updates simultaneously. AI automation goes beyond simple workflow tools to introduce intelligent decision-making into your business operations. Systems that can classify enquiries, draft client communications, extract data from documents, and route tasks to the right team member automatically. For Sevenoaks businesses operating at the premium end of the market, AI automation delivers the operational capacity of a much larger firm without the headcount.',
  'The Sevenoaks business environment is characterised by high-value, high-complexity operations managed by relatively small teams. Professional services firms handle complex regulatory requirements alongside client relationship management. Specialist trades manage intricate projects across the affluent residential district. Independent retailers balance inventory, customer service, and marketing with limited staff. The common thread is that operational complexity has outgrown team capacity. The twenty-four-minute London commute means many business owners have limited hours in the working day, making operational efficiency critical.',
  'AI automation is virtually unknown among Sevenoaks businesses, representing a genuine first-mover opportunity. While basic software tools are widely adopted, intelligent automation that uses AI to make decisions, classify information, and generate outputs is yet to penetrate this market. Early adopters will gain significant competitive advantages in operational efficiency and client service quality.',
  'We implement AI automation for Sevenoaks businesses by identifying the highest-value tasks where intelligent decision-making can replace manual effort. For professional services, this might mean AI-powered document review and client communication drafting. For trades, it could mean intelligent job scheduling and automated progress reporting. Every implementation is designed to augment your team''s capability rather than replace the personal service your Sevenoaks clientele values.',
  '{"population": 30000, "district_population": 120000, "business_districts": ["High Street", "London Road", "Bat & Ball area"], "key_fact": "High-complexity operations with small teams create ideal conditions for AI automation impact"}',
